---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Community | Wesichain"
  description="Join the Wesichain community, contribute, and get involved."
  variant="landing"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="mb-16 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl">Join the Wesichain Community</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-neutral-400">
        Wesichain is open source and built in public. We welcome contributions of all kinds.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/wesichain/wesichain"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="rounded-full bg-rust-600 px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-rust-700 transition-colors"
        >
          View on GitHub
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/wesichain/wesichain/discussions"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="rounded-full border border-neutral-700 bg-neutral-900 px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors"
        >
          Start a Discussion
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Quick links -->
    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3 mb-16">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/wesichain/wesichain/issues"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900 p-6 hover:border-neutral-700 transition-colors"
      >
        <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-rust-600/10">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-rust-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
            <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12" />
            <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-rust-400 transition-colors">GitHub Issues</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-neutral-500">Report bugs or request features</p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="https://github.com/wesichain/wesichain/discussions"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900 p-6 hover:border-neutral-700 transition-colors"
      >
        <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-rust-600/10">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-rust-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-rust-400 transition-colors">GitHub Discussions</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-neutral-500">Ask questions and share ideas</p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="https://github.com/wesichain/wesichain/blob/main/wesichain/ROADMAP.md"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900 p-6 hover:border-neutral-700 transition-colors"
      >
        <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-rust-600/10">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-rust-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M9 20l-5.447-2.724A1 1 0 0 1 3 16.382V5.618a1 1 0 0 1 1.447-.894L9 7m0 13l6-3m-6 3V7m6 10l4.553 2.276A1 1 0 0 0 21 18.382V7.618a1 1 0 0 0-1.447-.894L15 9m0 8V9m0 0L9 7" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-rust-400 transition-colors">Roadmap</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-neutral-500">See what's planned for v0.4+</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Contributing -->
    <section id="contributing" class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Contributing</h2>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-3">Dev Setup</h3>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 p-4">
            <pre class="text-sm text-neutral-300 overflow-x-auto"><code>{`# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/wesichain/wesichain.git
cd wesichain/wesichain

# Build all crates
cargo build

# Run all tests
cargo test

# Check formatting and lints (required before PR)
cargo fmt --check
cargo clippy -- -D warnings`}</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-3">Commit Conventions</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-3">
            All commits must follow <a href="https://www.conventionalcommits.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-rust-400 hover:text-rust-300">Conventional Commits</a> with a scope:
          </p>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 p-4">
            <pre class="text-sm text-neutral-300 overflow-x-auto"><code>{`feat(wesichain-agent): add parallel tool execution
fix(wesichain-graph): resolve checkpoint deserialization edge case
chore(workspace): bump tokio to 1.44`}</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-3">PR Workflow</h3>
          <ol class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-400 list-decimal list-inside">
            <li>Fork the repository and create a feature branch from <code class="rounded bg-neutral-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-neutral-200">main</code></li>
            <li>Make your changes with tests for all new functionality</li>
            <li>Run <code class="rounded bg-neutral-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-neutral-200">cargo fmt</code>, <code class="rounded bg-neutral-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-neutral-200">cargo clippy</code>, and <code class="rounded bg-neutral-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-neutral-200">cargo test</code> locally</li>
            <li>Open a PR with a description of what changed and why</li>
            <li>Address any review feedback</li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-3">Code Quality Requirements</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-400">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-rust-500 shrink-0">✓</span> Follow standard Rust naming conventions</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-rust-500 shrink-0">✓</span> Use <code class="rounded bg-neutral-800 px-1 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-neutral-200">async-trait</code> for async trait implementations</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-rust-500 shrink-0">✓</span> Tests required for all new public APIs</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-rust-500 shrink-0">✓</span> No new <code class="rounded bg-neutral-800 px-1 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-neutral-200">unwrap()</code> calls in library code — use <code class="rounded bg-neutral-800 px-1 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-neutral-200">?</code> and proper error types</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-rust-500 shrink-0">✓</span> <code class="rounded bg-neutral-800 px-1 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-neutral-200">cargo clippy -- -D warnings</code> must pass with zero warnings</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Code of Conduct -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Code of Conduct</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-4">
        We are committed to a welcoming and inclusive community. All participants are expected to follow our{' '}
        <a
          href="https://github.com/wesichain/wesichain/blob/main/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-rust-400 hover:text-rust-300"
        >
          Code of Conduct
        </a>.
        Key principles:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-400">
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-neutral-600 shrink-0">—</span> Be respectful and considerate in all interactions</li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-neutral-600 shrink-0">—</span> Critique ideas, not people</li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-neutral-600 shrink-0">—</span> Harassment and exclusionary behavior will not be tolerated</li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-neutral-600 shrink-0">—</span> Report violations via GitHub Issues or direct contact with maintainers</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Roadmap teaser -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">What's Next</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-6">
        v0.4 is focused on production hardening, expanded provider support, and a native Python SDK for interoperability.
        See the full{' '}
        <a
          href="https://github.com/wesichain/wesichain/blob/main/wesichain/ROADMAP.md"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-rust-400 hover:text-rust-300"
        >
          ROADMAP.md
        </a>
        for details.
      </p>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-3">v0.4 Highlights (planned)</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-400">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-neutral-600 shrink-0">—</span> OpenTelemetry distributed tracing across agents</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-neutral-600 shrink-0">—</span> Native Python bindings via PyO3</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-neutral-600 shrink-0">—</span> Multi-agent coordination primitives</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-neutral-600 shrink-0">—</span> Expanded vector store integrations (Pinecone, Milvus)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</SiteLayout>
